downscaleR 1.3-1
=================

* Added internal `make.names`in plot climatology to avoid duplicate panel names
* Bug fix in `getYearsAsINDEX` in annually aggregated grids
* Bug fix in dimnames attribute adjustment for single-year subsetting via `subsetGrid`
* New option in `makeMultiGrid`to skip temporal consistency checks
* Other minor bug fixes and enhancements



